    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped capers</strong>, <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong>, <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>salsa verde</strong></p>",
